OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPuberty blockers to be     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgiven only in clinical     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fresearch                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Puberty blockers will only be          
OL,6, prescribed to children attending gender
OL,7, identity services as part of clinical  
OL,8, research, NHS England has announced.   
OL,10,FThe move comes after an interim report 
OL,11,Finto children's gender services said   
OL,12,Fthere were "gaps in evidence" around   
OL,13,Fthe drugs.                             
OL,15,FBlockers are used to "pause puberty"   
OL,16,Fand work by supressing hormone release.
OL,18,FDr Hilary Cass's report called for a   
OL,19,Ftransformation in the model of care for
OL,20,Fchildren with gender-related distress. 
